Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.13,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}哪怕失去的恐懼作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:14.59,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}人們還是會走向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:16.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}看不見 不明白
